        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2Chronicles 29:25",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; and so may be understood to assert merely that the singing was in accordance with the arrangements of David and Asaph. (",
